k!help
Kotoba BOT 30-Dec-21 06:09 PM
Kotoba (page 1 of 3)
Say k!help CommandNameHere to see more information about a specific command.
k!jisho (short: k!j)
Search Jisho for an English or Japanese word. Example: k!j 少し
k!kanji (short: k!k)
Search for information about a kanji. Example: k!kanji 少
k!strokeorder (short: k!s, k!so)
Search for details about a kanji's strokes. Example: k!strokeorder 少
k!quiz (short: k!q)
See how to start a quiz in this channel.
k!jibiki (short: k!jb)
Search Jibiki for words, kanji and sentences. Example: k!jibiki 女らしい
k!weblio (short: k!w)
Search the Weblio Japanese dictionary for a word or phrase. Example: k!weblio 少し
k!shiritori (short: k!st, k!sh)
Start a game of shiritori in this channel.
k!help all
Show all commands on one page (good for pinning but long as xxx)
Links
Support Server | Web | GitHub
Kenuru can use the arrow reactions to see more commands.

Kotoba BOT 30-Dec-21 06:10 PM
Quiz
Say k!quiz deckname to start a quiz (Example: k!quiz N5). Say k!quiz stop to stop a quiz. Say nodelay after the deck name for a lightning fast quiz, for example: k!quiz N1 nodelay. For advanced help, say k!quiz help or visit me on the web.
